divs: Sighting DetailsOn the 8th and 9th of November starting at 7:15pm i saw and recorded 2 different objects in the sky each night.Two were oval,One was a cylinder shape and then looked triangular,The other one i dont know.The oval shaped objects appeared out of nowhere almost straight above two nights in a row and flew for a while and then disappeared.They were flying very slow.The cylinder appeared out of the northwest and was flying to the southeast.I was outside with my camcorder because we have been seeing unexplainable lights in the sky that fly for a while and then disappear.
Summary: On November 8th and 9th i recorded 2 different objects in the sky each night.
